"{\"uid\": \"dailyfreepress.com-03-26-21-203116-losing-the-linkedin-olympics-identity-unveiled\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"For college students in Boston, LinkedIn has evolved from a professional networking platform to a staple of everyday life.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9999999855845091, \"rank\": 1.4355959235233763e-08, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}, {\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The site, founded in 2002, was created to allow business professionals to increase business connections, search for jobs and look for new hires.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was introduced to LinkedIn during my senior year of high school.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My peers described the blue and white app as an \\\"Instagram for academics.\\\"\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with the changes to my school routine that COVID-19 pandemic brought on, I thought little about the platform.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999998266671505, \"rank\": 1.7214559319402943e-07, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a soon-to-be first generation college student, the pressure to navigate the college application process by myself was already more than I could bear.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon entering Boston University, I immediately scrambled to catch up to my seemingly more knowledgeable peers.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999998904059, \"rank\": 1.0944659903669875e-10, \"text\": \"Boston University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a city with some of the most prestigious universities in the world, I took the first step to \\\"fit in\\\" by creating a LinkedIn account.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recall devoting an unreasonable amount of time to curate the perfect profile.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I rummaged through the internet for LinkedIn tips in a desperate attempt to exaggerate my lackluster resume.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wondered if recruiters could tell that my headshot was a zoomed-in group photo of me with a blouse edited in, and that's the reason why they did not respond to my cold message.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the course of my undergraduate career, my connections grew steadily, but my activity on LinkedIn gradually declined in turn.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I found myself burdened with the weight of my acquaintances' impressive achievements whenever I scrolled through the app.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be honest, I do not even know half of my connections personally - I am willing to bet that most college students with 500 plus connections do not either.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Think of it this way: a person would never openly brag about their accomplishments to strangers they have never met, much less announce it to everyone within ears reach.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn normalizes just that, as the platform literally has a built-in notification option for sharing any updates with all existing connections.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn mirrors every other social media platform in setting a stage for comparison.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of admiring an influencer's lifestyle on Instagram, I hyperfixate on my peers' career accomplishments on LinkedIn.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.521815315362938e-33, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I compare myself to them through internship experience and GPA, and pay the price with my peace of mind.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3655098001629994e-12, \"text\": \"GPA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My insecurities are amplified - and I feel obligated to keep it to myself.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The LinkedIn community demands positivity and support, so feeling bitter about a peer's achievements breaks an unspoken code of professionalism.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The irony lies in the fact that by being a part of the LinkedIn community, individuals are inadvertently contributing to the same environment that fosters feelings of jealousy and inadequacy for themselves.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2629, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially for first-generation college students battling imposter syndrome, LinkedIn can be alienating.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn's promotion of hustle culture is a capitalist's ultimate fantasy.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pervasive \\\"rise and grind\\\" mentality that one must only devote themselves to work and sacrifice everything outside of it exists to pressure people into tying their self-worth to their career pursuits.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels as though hobbies that do not align with career ambitions are worthless and any leisure time should be utilized to work even harder.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A relentless fixation on productivity only pushes us to become soulless machines.\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no winning the LinkedIn Olympics, yet we still try.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crucial to understand that success should not come at the expense of someone's mental well-being.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is important to concentrate on genuine personal improvement rather than being engrossed in endless comparison.\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no one-size-fits-all recipe for success - a personal balance is key.\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your donation will support the student journalists of Boston University.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999998904059, \"rank\": 1.0944659903669875e-10, \"text\": \"Boston University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your contribution will allow us to purchase equipment and cover our annual website hosting costs.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel reply  Your email address will not be published.Required fields are marked*  Comment*  Name*  Email*\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 4030, \"entities\": []}]}"